  "slug": "what-did-thirty-nine-year-old-me-believe-about-forty",
  "title": "What Did Thirty-Nine-Year-Old Me Believe About Forty?",
  "subtitle": "A journal practice for examining what you believed this age would feel like before you arrived",
  "excerpt": "A journal practice for comparing the 40 you imagined in advance with the 40 you are actually living. For the gap between anticipation and experience, and for updating the story about what this decade is.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Written for homemade.education.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A journal practice for examining the age you expected versus the age you have. The beliefs about what 40 (or 50, or 60) would feel like are usually formed at a distance: a mixture of cultural messages, early observations of older women, and projection. By the time the decade arrives, the picture is almost never what was imagined. This practice examines the distance.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to journal prompts? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "journal prompts as practice",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/journal-prompts-as-practice"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Warm-up",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What did you believe about this age before you reached it?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write what you thought 40 (or the relevant decade) would look like: how you expected to feel, what you assumed you'd have, who you thought you'd be.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Closer in",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where did those beliefs come from?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Older women you observed? Films and television? Something a parent said? The culture at the time you were forming these ideas? Be specific about the source.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "How does the actual experience compare?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What is better than you expected? What is worse? What is simply different? Write the comparison without editing toward a positive or negative conclusion.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What beliefs from that earlier version of you are you still carrying that no longer apply?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The old story about what this age means. Write what you are ready to let go of.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where this practice comes from",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
